title: Regulator V2 ICE TEC1 DIR Set - EN250A

photos.alt: Automat V2 ICE TEC1 DIR Set - EN250A

description:
Product description

Set of regulators based on the Tecline V2 ICE first stages:
- Certified according to EN250 A norm for cold water (recommended for ice diving)
- Perfect hoses routing in the double tank configuration (twinset)
- More information about the V-Series: https://teclinediving.eu/v-series-regulators

The set consists of:
- 2x I stage V2 ICE
- 2x II stage TEC1
- Hoses*:
LP 2,10m Proflex black
LP 0,61m Proflex black
- Bolt Snap 88mm
- Rubber bungee for backup regulator
- Tecline bag

 * choose the color, length and type of hoses in the set!
Contact your local Tecline Dealer and place your order now: https://teclinediving.eu/store-locator
